## Core Metrics (Appear Throughout the Site)

- **Î´_H (Collapse Index)** â€” System stress/fragility score from 0.00 to 1.00. Critical threshold: 0.52. Above 0.52 = collapse risk. Color coding: GREEN (0-0.30), GOLD (0.30-0.50), RED (0.50+)
- **MCS (Mereological Coherence Score)** â€” Analysis quality/coherence score from 0.00 to 1.00. Our threshold: â‰¥0.90 for published work
- **Orric** â€” Paradox density/ontological risk index. High Orric = stuck contradictions requiring resolution
- **LSSE (Latent Structural Stress Energy)** â€” Measures hidden stress in a system before it manifests
- **PL Score (Perceptual Light)** â€” Propaganda/manipulation measurement. 0.00 = clean information, 1.00 = pure propaganda

