## Tech Stack

```
Framework:      Next.js 14+ (App Router)
Language:       TypeScript
Styling:        Tailwind CSS
3D/WebGL:       Three.js + @react-three/fiber + @react-three/drei (lazy-loaded)
Animation:      GSAP + ScrollTrigger (primary), Framer Motion (secondary)
Micro-viz:      Raw SVG + CSS keyframes
Fonts:          Space Grotesk, Inter, JetBrains Mono (via Google Fonts or next/font)
Icons:          Lucide React
Deployment:     Vercel
```

