## Key Visual Components

### Hero Treatment (All Pages)

- Full viewport height
- WebGL mesh gradient background (4 color blobs, sinusoidal motion, 20-30s cycle)
- Gradient adapts color per page (accent color system above)
- Character-level text reveal animation on hero heading (MorphÃ© easing)
- Word-level text reveal on subheading (LumiÃ¨re easing)
- Subtle noise texture overlay at 3% opacity (Velum)

### CAPS Network Visualization

- 6 nodes in hexagonal arrangement: Perplexity, Claude, Gemini, ChatGPT, Grok, Notion AI (9)
- Animated connection lines showing data flow between AIs
- Sequential pulse animation (30s cycle): scan â†’ validate â†’ formalize â†’ critique â†’ implement â†’ integrate
- Center convergence pulse (gold) = "Metallic Pulse" moment
- Pure SVG + CSS, no Three.js

### Solvey Î´_H Heatmap

- Flat 2D SVG world map with pulsing hotspot circles
- Color-coded by Î´_H severity (green â†’ teal â†’ gold â†’ orange â†’ red)
- Radar-style scanning line sweeps horizontally
- Dashed constraint lines connecting related hotspots
- Hover tooltips with region name + Î´_H value + status

### PEE-Î© Text Scanner

- Mock text block with propaganda sample
- Animated scan line sweeps through text
- Keywords highlight red with manipulation type labels
- Running counter: "Manipulation Score" incrementing
- Final verdict with colored border glow

### Report Generation Pipeline

- 5-stage horizontal pipeline: Ingestion â†’ Processing â†’ Analysis â†’ Synthesis â†’ Delivery
- Each stage animates in sequence (20s cycle)
- Active stage glows, others dimmed
- Counters animate: source count, Î´_H gauge, MCS score, delivery timer

