## What "Advanced" Means for This Site

This is not a template site. This should feel like:

- **Stripe** (technical elegance, WebGL sophistication, developer-grade precision)
- **A private intelligence dashboard** (dark, data-rich, observatory-like)
- **An Awwwards Site of the Year** (scroll-driven reveals, micro-interactions, custom cursor)
- **A haute couture lookbook** (dark room photography, chrome metal, shadow-as-design)

Every animation serves meaning. Nothing is decorative noise. Constraint breeds resonance.